  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in Totolink N300RH 6.1c.1353_B20190305. Affected by this issue is the function setWiFiBasicConfig of the file wireless.so of the component Web Management Interface. Performing a manipulation of the argument KeyStr results in stack-based buffer overflow. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used.",
